snippet.title: 👗👒Garden & Dressup - Flower Princess Fairytale
snippet.description:
Dress up your own little sweetheart!

The magic garden is opening now, and come here to waiting for the flower princess! In this magic world, you can not only plant different kinds of flowers, but dress up the little princess. At the same time, you can also make up the princess and make your princess be the most shining star!
